t:authprovider-resetpass-skip-label}}\" to change it later.\";'),('en','messages:resetpass-wrong-oldpass','s:123:\"en:Invalid temporary or current password.\nYou may have already changed your password or requested a new temporary password.\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_announce','s:53:\"en:To finish logging in, you must set a new password.\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_forbidden','s:30:\"en:Passwords cannot be changed\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_forbidden-reason','s:34:\"en:Passwords cannot be changed: $1\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_header','s:26:\"en:Change account password\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_submit','s:26:\"en:Set password and log in\";'),('en','messages:resetpass_text','s:25:\"en:<!-- Add text here -->\";'),('en','messages:resettokens','s:15:\"en:Reset tokens\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-done','s:16:\"en:Tokens reset.\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-no-tokens','s:32:\"en:There are no tokens to reset.\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-resetbutton','s:24:\"en:Reset selected tokens\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-summary','s:3:\"en:\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-text','s:205:\"en:You can reset tokens which allow access to certain private data associated with your account here.\n\nYou should do it if you accidentally shared them with someone or if your account has been compromised.\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-token-label','s:25:\"en:$1 (current value: $2)\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-tokens','s:10:\"en:Tokens:\";'),('en','messages:resettokens-watchlist-token','s:96:\"en:Token for the web feed (Atom/RSS) of [[Special:Watchlist|changes to pages on your watchlist]]\";'),('en','messages:rest-bad-content-model','s:24:\"en:Bad content model: $1\";'),('en','messages:rest-bad-etag','s:15:\"en:Bad ETag: $1\";'),('en','messages:rest-bad-json-body','s:43:\"en:Bad request body, must be a JSON object.\";'),('en','messages:rest-bad-prefix','s:64:\"en:The endpoint path ($1) does not contain a valid module prefix\";'),('en','messages:rest-bad-stash-key','s:17:\"en:Bad stash key.\";'),('en','messages:rest-badtoken','s:38:\"en:The CSRF token provided is invalid.\";'),('en','messages:rest-badtoken-missing','s:93:\"en:The <var>token</var> parameter is required unless using a CSRF-safe authentication method.\";'),('en','messages:rest-badtoken-nosession','s:27:\"en:CSRF error - no session.\";'),('en','messages:rest-body-validation-error','s:27:\"en:Invalid request body: $1\";'),('en','messages:rest-cannot-load-file','s:44:\"en:The file for title \"$1\" cannot be loaded.\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-inaccessible','s:73:\"en:The revision specified by the $1 parameter is not publicly accessible.\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-nonexistent','s:61:\"en:The revision specified by the $1 parameter does not exist.\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-page-mismatch','s:79:\"en:The specified revisions belong to different pages; refusing to compare them.\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-permission-denied','s:54:\"en:User doesn\'t have access to the requested revisions\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-wikidiff2','s:51:\"en:This endpoint requires wikidiff2 1.9.0 or later.\";'),('en','messages:rest-compare-wrong-content','s:114:\"en:The $1 slot of the revision specified by the $2 parameter has a content type which cannot be converted to text.\";'),('en','messages:rest-cross-origin-anon-write','s:56:\"en:Anonymous cross-origin write requests are not allowed\";'),('en','messages:rest-edit-conflict','s:21:\"en:Edit conflict ($1)\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-file-title','s:118:\"en:Returns information about a file, including links to download the file in thumbnail, preview, and original formats.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-history','s:259:\"en:Returns information about the latest revisions to a page, in segments of 20 revisions, starting with the latest revision. The response includes URLs to get the next oldest, next newest, and latest revision segments, letting you scroll through page history.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-history-counts','s:274:\"en:Returns data about a page\'s history, such as the number of edits made by different types of users. For more data about how readers and editors interact with Wikimedia projects, see the [Analytics API](https://doc.wikimedia.org/generated-data-platform/aqs/analytics-api/).\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title','s:84:\"en:Returns information about a page, including the page source, usually in wikitext.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-bare','s:36:\"en:Returns information about a page.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-html','s:41:\"en:Returns the content of a page in HTML.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-language','s:58:\"en:Lists pages with the same topic in different languages.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-lint','s:38:\"en:Returns the lint errors for a page.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-media','s:53:\"en:Lists media files used on a page, up to 100 files.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-with-html','s:72:\"en:Returns information about a page, including the page content in HTML.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-compare','s:132:\"en:Returns information that lets you display a line-by-line comparison of two revisions. Only text-based wiki pages can be compared.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id','s:92:\"en:Returns information about a revision, including the revision source, usually in wikitext.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-bare','s:40:\"en:Returns information about a revision.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-html','s:45:\"en:Returns the content of a revision in HTML.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-lint','s:42:\"en:Returns the lint errors for a revision.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-with-html','s:80:\"en:Returns information about a revision, including the revision content in HTML.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search','s:116:\"en:Returns an [OpenSearch description document](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/XML/Guides/OpenSearch).\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search-page','s:47:\"en:Lists pages matching the given search terms.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search-title','s:157:\"en:Lists pages with titles that begin with the given search terms. You can use this endpoint as an autocomplete search that suggests relevant pages by title.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-mock-desc','s:20:\"en:Mock description.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-page','s:18:\"en:Creates a page.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-html-to-wikitext','s:31:\"en:Converts HTML into wikitext.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-html-to-wikitext-title','s:177:\"en:Converts HTML into wikitext. The html request body parameter must be provided, but can be empty to receive the full page. The response body contains the wikitext of the page.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-html-to-wikitext-title-revision','s:212:\"en:Converts the HTML of a given revision to wikitext. The html request body parameter must be provided, but can be left empty to receive the full revision. The response body contains the Wikitext of the revision.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-wikitext-to-html','s:31:\"en:Converts wikitext into HTML.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-wikitext-to-html-title','s:191:\"en:Converts wikitext into HTML. The wikitext request body parameter must be provided, but can be left empty to receive the full page. The response body contains the rendered HTML of the page.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-wikitext-to-html-title-revision','s:221:\"en:Converts the wikitext of a given revision to HTML. The wikitext request body parameter must be provided, but can be left empty to receive the full revision. The response body contains the rendered HTML of the revision.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-wikitext-to-lint','s:35:\"en:Returns lint errors for wikitext\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-put-page-title','s:273:\"en:Edits a page based on the page\'s latest revision identifier, or creates a page if no revision identifier is given. If there is a merge conflict, the API attempts to resolve the conflict automatically. If the edit conflict cannot be resolved, the API returns a 409 error.\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-file-title','s:11:\"en:Get file\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-history','s:19:\"en:Get page history\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-history-counts','s:26:\"en:Get page history counts\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title','s:18:\"en:Get page source\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-bare','s:11:\"en:Get page\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-html','s:11:\"en:Get HTML\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-language','s:16:\"en:Get languages\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-lint','s:23:\"en:Get page lint errors\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-media','s:20:\"en:Get files on page\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-page-title-with-html','s:21:\"en:Get page with HTML\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-revision-compare','s:20:\"en:Compare revisions\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-revision-id','s:22:\"en:Get revision source\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-revision-id-bare','s:15:\"en:Get revision\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-revision-id-html','s:20:\"en:Get revision HTML\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-revision-id-lint','s:27:\"en:Get revision lint errors\";'),('en','messages:rest-endpoint-summ-get-re