cceso a la revisiÃģn solicitada\";'),('es','messages:rest-compare-wikidiff2','s:52:\"es:Este endpoint requiere wikidiff2 1.9.0 o superor.\";'),('es','messages:rest-compare-wrong-content','s:128:\"es:El espacio $1 de la revisiÃģn especificada por el parÃĄmetro $2 tiene un tipo de contenido que no se puede convertir a texto.\";'),('es','messages:rest-cross-origin-anon-write','s:56:\"en:Anonymous cross-origin write requests are not allowed\";'),('es','messages:rest-edit-conflict','s:21:\"en:Edit conflict ($1)\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-file-title','s:118:\"en:Returns information about a file, including links to download the file in thumbnail, preview, and original formats.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-history','s:259:\"en:Returns information about the latest revisions to a page, in segments of 20 revisions, starting with the latest revision. The response includes URLs to get the next oldest, next newest, and latest revision segments, letting you scroll through page history.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-history-counts','s:274:\"en:Returns data about a page\'s history, such as the number of edits made by different types of users. For more data about how readers and editors interact with Wikimedia projects, see the [Analytics API](https://doc.wikimedia.org/generated-data-platform/aqs/analytics-api/).\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title','s:84:\"en:Returns information about a page, including the page source, usually in wikitext.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-bare','s:36:\"en:Returns information about a page.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-html','s:41:\"en:Returns the content of a page in HTML.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-language','s:58:\"en:Lists pages with the same topic in different languages.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-lint','s:38:\"en:Returns the lint errors for a page.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-media','s:53:\"en:Lists media files used on a page, up to 100 files.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-page-title-with-html','s:72:\"en:Returns information about a page, including the page content in HTML.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-compare','s:132:\"en:Returns information that lets you display a line-by-line comparison of two revisions. Only text-based wiki pages can be compared.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id','s:92:\"en:Returns information about a revision, including the revision source, usually in wikitext.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-bare','s:40:\"en:Returns information about a revision.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-html','s:45:\"en:Returns the content of a revision in HTML.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-lint','s:42:\"en:Returns the lint errors for a revision.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-revision-id-with-html','s:80:\"en:Returns information about a revision, including the revision content in HTML.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search','s:116:\"en:Returns an [OpenSearch description document](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/XML/Guides/OpenSearch).\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search-page','s:47:\"en:Lists pages matching the given search terms.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-get-search-title','s:157:\"en:Lists pages with titles that begin with the given search terms. You can use this endpoint as an autocomplete search that suggests relevant pages by title.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-mock-desc','s:20:\"en:Mock description.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-page','s:18:\"en:Creates a page.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-html-to-wikitext','s:31:\"en:Converts HTML into wikitext.\";'),('es','messages:rest-endpoint-desc-post-transform-html-to-wikitext-title','s:177:\"en:Converts HTML 